blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有 同樣百幾二百ping</blockquote><br />\n有無用咩方法加速或者壓低個ping?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇 同埋我用macbook黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> macbook都可以200以下<br />\n我即刻開黎試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔知你delay到咩情況 但正常有些少遲鈍就梗既"},{"pid":"a4e8c88ccb65b99ba633fc0bbc3d78bd298812d6","tid":110503,"uid":80612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:46:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ping 最低都20x，香港去美國始終有段路程<br />\n但係穩定咁20x係無問題，唔穩定／delay 係isp設定上有問題<br />\n可以打電話叫isp fix <br />\n你sure硬件無問題（打台服冇事）<br />\n打美服會delay 一秒就可以叫isp整野<br />\n通常一日左右，記得話佢知你打咩game同咩server</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e97fe3e8dfa6a8bf15b4fa73db3cb05bf0bef75","tid":110503,"uid":12518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:46:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc732ba26b47ffbafd166a2ae760cb160ff1dd07","tid":110503,"uid":80612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有 同樣百幾二百ping</blockquote><br />\n有無用咩方法加速或者壓低個ping?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇 同埋我用macbook黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> macbook都可以200以下<br />\n我即刻開黎試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔知你delay到咩情況 但正常有些少遲鈍就梗既</blockquote><br />\ndelay成秒呀 我知delay係好正常 但只係想知道下會唔會有咩方法可以打得無咁辛苦姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw macbook開 500幾ping 我可以慳返啖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3700cc027fd6ec294924effb7a8fe65665155db3","tid":110503,"uid":80612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前一路都170左右<br />\n<br />\n自從美服轉芝加哥server我就220以上<br />\n<br />\n而家玩美服要特登揸架遊艇出西貢玩...可以低20ping左右</blockquote><br />\n佢轉左去芝加哥之後我270-300ping<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就轉左玩台服<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家用左加速已經無個陣咁誇張 但都係delay成秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bfe48d1506b294969d982c075e621f0b6e24fc","tid":110503,"uid":42952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前一路都170左右<br />\n<br />\n自從美服轉芝加哥server我就220以上<br />\n<br />\n而家玩美服要特登揸架遊艇出西貢玩...可以低20ping左右</blockquote><br />\n佢轉左去芝加哥之後我270-300ping<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就轉左玩台服<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家用左加速已經無個陣咁誇張 但都係delay成秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你台服係順，而美服delay一秒，就係isp setting 問題，你點搞都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b07f1d84098e435c4db14a64be9598d4ee786bc","tid":110503,"uid":18721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前一路都170左右<br />\n<br />\n自從美服轉芝加哥server我就220以上<br />\n<br />\n而家玩美服要特登揸架遊艇出西貢玩...可以低20ping左右</blockquote><br />\n啱啊 之前宇轉server頂多都係150-170<br />\n轉撚左芝加哥冇200都唔好諗<br />\n咁撚高ping好多操作都冇得做<br />\n唔好話lee sin R flash<br />\n連yasuo 升盡左招E都連唔到dash 不撚柒知所謂"},{"pid":"1c259ae532a39abb7e70b1373abe8187092b8f57","tid":110503,"uid":80612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前一路都170左右<br />\n<br />\n自從美服轉芝加哥server我就220以上<br />\n<br />\n而家玩美服要特登揸架遊艇出西貢玩...可以低20ping左右</blockquote><br />\n佢轉左去芝加哥之後我270-300ping<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就轉左玩台服<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /